item.title: CVE-2023-28069|2024-08-02T12:30:24.147Z -- dell -- streaming%20data%20platform
item.description: Dell Streaming Data Platform prior to 1.4 contains Open Redirect vulnerability. A remote unauthenticated attacker can phish the legitimate user to redirect to malicious website leading to information disclosure and launch of phishing attacks.
